Paper: hep-th/9511054

Date: 1995-11-08

Title: Bilayers in Four Dimensions and Supersymmetry

Diderot, Paris, France)Comments: 4 pages,Latex, no figure

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A11 (1996) 277-280

I build $N=1$ superstrings in $\Bbb R^4$ out of purely geometric bosonicdata. The world-sheet is a bilayer of uniform thickness and the $2D$supercharge vanishes in a natural way.